msg: added a test case from Neil Thorne which dug up a few different issues such as arrays were not properly being iterated over by the splitter and XPath expressions which were not properly evaluating things like a/b to all the matching values, just the first string matched value. For more details see: http://www.nabble.com/Problem-with-XPath-splitters-tf4357605s22882.html#a12418572
